{"tid":1669381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4狼死南亞雌雄賊偷竊如掃貨　擸走金舖84隻金戒指","createTime":"2019-10-22T13:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T15:58:49.000Z","uid":78947,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"99d95340d0116f81c6a11167124c6db340674fd1","tid":1669381,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"南亞幫又作奸犯科，偷走金行總值17萬元金器。昨日(20日)傍晚6時許，3名南亞裔男子偕同一名南亞裔女子，步進筲箕灣筲箕灣道368號一間金飾店，佯裝購買金飾，期間着姓林(51歲)女負責人展示一批金器，各人觀賞一番後未有幫襯便離開。詎料，林隨後發現店內1盆共84隻總值17萬港元的金戒指不翼而飛，懷疑是該批南亞裔男女所為，大驚報警求助。<br />\n警員到場調查，並將案列作盜竊，交由東區警區刑事調查隊跟進，正根據店舖負責人提供資料及天眼片段追查賊人下落。4日前(18日)，4名南亞裔男子連同一名南亞裔女子，假扮豪客，到達元朗朗日路8號形點二期一間珠寶店，趁機偷走一顆約值36萬元鑽石，由於兩案手法相近，警方不排除同一幫賊人所為，正就案件深入調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191021/bkn-20191021041520272-1021_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191021%2Fbkn-20191021041520272-1021_00822_001.html&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=0b3adb03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191021/bkn-20191021041520272-1021_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4ce6dee89228b60666cf516d0f2d634dbc8920b9","tid":1669381,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ccf57d59ce30915bec9deb06c774c7ab13dc34","tid":1669381,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0949686284be7edce8b9389ade12d6388bdab474","tid":1669381,"uid":85852,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:50:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>南亞幫又作奸犯科</strong></span></span>算唔算種族歧視？"},{"pid":"1449120e7d905c83489786e3b209d300f256db70","tid":1669381,"uid":19055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy